<h1>Verify your email address</h1>
<p>
    Hi, <%= name %>!
    Thank you for registering with us. To complete your registration, please click on the button below to verify your
    email address:
</p>
<p>
    <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" target="_blank">
        <button
